title: Minted SF Block Party
description:
MINTED SF Week 12 – Dirty Not Sorry

September 19 @ 5:00 pm - 9:00 PM - **Free**

MINTED SF is San Francisco’s new Friday night Happy Hour experience – a free, all-ages celebration of music, food, and community lighting up Downtown San Francisco’s historic Mint Plaza all Summer long. From July 4 to September 19, 2025, the Bay Area’s top DJs and music culture makers are partnering with local restaurants to transform the plaza into a vibrant open-air dance floor and culinary hotspot.
